		font-size: 14px;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		text-align: center;
		justify-content: center;
		white-space: normal;
	}

	/* the specific check (or sanction) reason, in the anticheat red. */
	.test-reason {
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #ff8c69;
		text-align: center;
		justify-content: center;
		white-space: normal;
